Name: djangocms-simple-accordion
Version: 0.1.0
Summary: Django-CMS Plugin for accordion tabs. It's easy to style and does not rely on big dependencies
Home-page: https://github.com/Blueshoe/djangocms-simple-accordion
Author: Maximilian Muth
